- [ Grunting ]
- The radiation--
Get out of here.

36:57.783 --> 36:59.818
You first!

37:03.221 --> 37:04.990
[ Grunting Continues ]

37:18.404 --> 37:20.339
[ Cell Phone Beeping ]

37:20.372 --> 37:22.808
Snake Doc here.

37:22.841 --> 37:24.776
It's done. It's over.

37:24.810 --> 37:28.179
[ Cheering ]

37:28.213 --> 37:30.582
[ Bridget On Speakerphone ]
The bomb has been neutralized.

37:30.616 --> 37:34.119
[ Relieved Sighs,
Chattering ]
That's it. Good work.

37:34.152 --> 37:36.422
Dodged a bullet,
didn't we?

37:38.056 --> 37:39.891
[ Chattering ]

37:47.833 --> 37:49.835
[ Man ]
37th Fighter Wing confirms,
Mr. President.

37:49.868 --> 37:51.837
Scrambled a squadron
of B-2s out of Panama.

37:51.870 --> 37:54.906
They'll be over Caracas
in an hour.

37:54.940 --> 37:56.975
We'll see then if our friend
in Venezuela owns up.

37:57.008 --> 37:59.277
Sir, if you want my team--
Thank you, Sergeant Major.

37:59.311 --> 38:01.980
We've got it covered here.

38:02.013 --> 38:04.983
We're also getting further
intel from the Russians.

38:05.016 --> 38:07.586
Mr. President,
Kochenko was right
about one thing.

38:07.619 --> 38:09.621
The assassination attempt.
Yes, sir.

38:11.056 --> 38:14.626
God knows
what else I've inherited
I don't know about yet.

38:14.660 --> 38:17.796
- Sir, any responsibility for--
- Yes. I understand.

38:20.699 --> 38:25.036
Sergeant Major, your country
appreciates all you've done.

38:25.070 --> 38:27.373
Thank you, Mr. President.

38:37.015 --> 38:39.985
You still got something
you need to sort out,
Sergeant Major?

38:40.018 --> 38:43.254
You know where I stand, Colonel.
There ain't a pulpit
big enough to--

38:43.288 --> 38:45.557
You lied to us,
and that cannot pass.

38:45.591 --> 38:48.994
That lie saved you, me
and a hell of a lot of people.
So what's that make me?

38:49.027 --> 38:51.530
A brigadier general.

38:53.765 --> 38:56.935
Do you think I'm not fit
to command the Unit?

39:01.407 --> 39:03.409
You know it.

39:03.442 --> 39:05.544
The Russians know it.

39:07.178 --> 39:09.981
Sometimes the man
looking in the mirror is
the last one to know it.

39:11.249 --> 39:13.419
As long as he finally
figures it out.

39:21.860 --> 39:23.995
See, there's one
right there.
Yeah. I see it.

39:24.029 --> 39:28.099
You know what that is?
Not exactly. I'd like
to see a little bit more.

39:28.133 --> 39:31.102
Can we zoom in
on that right there?
Yeah.

39:36.975 --> 39:39.244
Could I have a minute?

39:39.277 --> 39:41.112
Are you addressing me?

39:43.515 --> 39:45.717
Warrant Officer,
with permission.

39:55.827 --> 39:58.964
What is it?
Look, I gotta say something.

39:58.997 --> 40:00.632
Yes?

40:00.666 --> 40:02.834
I am sorry about
what occurred between us.

40:04.503 --> 40:08.006
I read the report, Sergeant.
You were just doing as ordered
for your cover.

40:09.441 --> 40:11.342
That doesn't quite fix it,
does it?

40:11.376 --> 40:13.178
No. Not quite.

40:18.283 --> 40:20.752
No. I suppose it doesn't.

40:21.720 --> 40:23.655
I appreciate
the words though.

